# Signal Lab Stack Rules

- Use Next.js App Router, NestJS, Prisma, PostgreSQL, Prometheus, Loki, Grafana, and Sentry only.
- Preserve `POST /api/scenarios`, `GET /api/scenarios`, and `GET /metrics`.
- Keep Grafana reachable both at `http://localhost:3002` and proxied via `http://localhost:3000/grafana`.
- Keep Sentry optional via `SENTRY_DSN`.
